      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, add the <strong>cooked farfalle</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up so everything is evenly coated – this is your <strong>creamy mangetout & spinach farfalle</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your pasta is looking a little dry!</p>",
      "order": 7,
